Package: astade
Section: devel
Priority: optional
Architecture: i386 amd64
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Recommends: graphviz, trace2uml, astadedraw, astadetools
Suggests: doxygen, doxygen-gui
Description: UML tool for C++ code generation
 Astade is a tool for model-based development and
 includes C and C++ code generators with Doxygen
 integration, an automatic Object Model Diagram
 generator, several state-machine generators,
 and more.

Package: astadedraw
Section: devel
Priority: optional
Architecture: i386 amd64
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: UML tool for drawing usecase and component diagrams
 AstadeDraw is a GUI program to draw usecase and component diagrams.
 
Package: astadegraphlib
Section: devel
Priority: optional
Architecture: i386 amd64
Depends: ${misc:Depends}
Description: Library for graphic programs similar to AstadeDraw
 astadegraphlib is a C++ library which contains everything
 necessary for graphic programs. It uses the engine devloped
 for AstadeDraw.
 If you don't plan to develop graphic programs in C++ yourself
 using this graphic engine, you don't need this package.

