Section: devel
Priority: optional
Architecture: i386 amd64
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Recommends: make
Suggests: doxygen, doxygen-gui
Description: UML tool for C++ code generation
 Astade is a tool for model-based development and
